{"tid":1479284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普與杜魯多通話談及香港局勢發展","createTime":"2019-08-16T23:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:12:33.000Z","uid":50457,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3eeedc1f2cd9587c426703d38ce4a0c65107c02","tid":1479284,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:55:20.000Z","msg":"17/8/2019 7:06<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;美國總統特朗普和加拿大總理杜魯多, 討論香港的示威事件, 及兩個加拿大人仍被中國政府扣押的事件.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;杜魯多的辦公室發聲明, 指兩位領袖討論與中國的關係, 包括香港的局勢發展, 及持續扣押兩個加拿大人.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;香港的示威由和平開始, 到近期演變成暴力衝突, 受到國際社會關注, 多國領袖紛紛置評. 另外, 中國電訊設備生產商華為的副董事長孟晚舟在加拿大被捕, 中國扣押境內兩個加拿大人, 令到兩國關係持續緊張.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;特朗普和杜魯多在通話中, 雙方重申支持新的北美自由貿易協議, 期望本國議會通過有關協議.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190817070649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190817070649&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75VNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=bd3beca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190817070649</a>"},{"pid":"6f6edf8446ee2de59ec6ec50c8bbaa853902a568","tid":1479284,"uid":24308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:58:00.000Z","msg":"條左膠依家都一身蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6521bd4fee819c0828ac892534fba2aba612ac0b","tid":1479284,"uid":20291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"正，收撚翻哂班垃圾國藉"},{"pid":"675afaf53528a8d72af68cc9167fc5db38f69287","tid":1479284,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:01:52.000Z","msg":"香港有幾十萬加拿大籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif